gies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Facts-About-WordPress-01-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Facts-About-WordPress-01-1-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-517508d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"517508d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 id=\"wordpress-benefits-in-2022\">WordPress Benefits in 2024<\/h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a51fafe elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a51fafe\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>DO YOU KNOW NEARLY 32.3% OF THE ALL WEBSITES ARE POWERED BY WORDPRESS?<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"look\">Now, let\u2019s take a deeper look as why you should consider none other than WordPress for your website development project. Here are the benefits of using wordpress.<\/p><h3 id=\"1-wordpress-is-free\">1: WordPress Is Free<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b1a15ca elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b1a15ca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">The #1 Benefit of wordpress is \u201cIt&#8217;s Free\u201d. WordPress doesn\u2019t cost you even a penny. It simply means that you can\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/download\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">download<\/a>, install and use it without paying anything. Another thing is that you can build any kind of website through it.<\/p><p>You just need a domain name and web hosting plan and you\u2019re good to go.<\/p><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-20760\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/undraw_Domain_names_re_0uun-300x194.png\" alt=\"Domain\" width=\"300\" height=\"194\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/undraw_Domain_names_re_0uun-300x194.png 300w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/undraw_Domain_names_re_0uun-1024x662.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/undraw_Domain_names_re_0uun-768x496.png 768w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/undraw_Domain_names_re_0uun.png 1029w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/figure>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9d74f57 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9d74f57\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">A domain name is nothing but the name of your website. For example, it is the text we type into address bar to open a particular website \u2013 www.xyz.com, www.rankontechnologies.com and others. Web hosting refers to your website\u2019s place where all relevant files are stored.<\/p><p class=\"look\">If you need assistance regarding this, we at RankOn are always on our toes to help you in the best possible manner.<\/p><p class=\"look\">Though you can choose to do it yourself, it is always recommended to choose a professional WordPress expert for the job.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-505b038 elementor-widget elementor-widget-video\" data-id=\"505b038\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;youtube_url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/youtu.be\\\/BgPKPGrkTMU&quot;,&quot;video_type&quot;:&quot;youtube&quot;,&quot;controls&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"video.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.18.0 - 20-12-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-video .elementor-widget-container{overflow:hidden;transform:translateZ(0)}.elementor-widget-video .elementor-wrapper{aspect-ratio:var(--video-aspect-ratio)}.elementor-widget-video .elementor-wrapper iframe,.elementor-widget-video .elementor-wrapper video{height:100%;width:100%;display:flex;border:none;background-color:#000}@supports not (aspect-ratio:1\/1){.elementor-widget-video .elementor-wrapper{position:relative;overflow:hidden;height:0;padding-bottom:calc(100% \/ var(--video-aspect-ratio))}.elementor-widget-video .elementor-wrapper iframe,.elementor-widget-video .elementor-wrapper video{position:absolute;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;left:0}}.elementor-widget-video .elementor-open-inline .elementor-custom-embed-image-overlay{position:absolute;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;left:0;background-size:cover;background-position:50%}.elementor-widget-video .elementor-custom-embed-image-overlay{cursor:pointer;text-align:center}.elementor-widget-video .elementor-custom-embed-image-overlay:hover .elementor-custom-embed-play i{opacity:1}.elementor-widget-video .elementor-custom-embed-image-overlay img{display:block;width:100%;aspect-ratio:var(--video-aspect-ratio);-o-object-fit:cover;object-fit:cover;-o-object-position:center center;object-position:center center}@supports not (aspect-ratio:1\/1){.elementor-widget-video .elementor-custom-embed-image-overlay{position:relative;overflow:hidden;height:0;padding-bottom:calc(100% \/ var(--video-aspect-ratio))}.elementor-widget-video .elementor-custom-embed-image-overlay img{position:absolute;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;left:0}}.elementor-widget-video .e-hosted-video .elementor-video{-o-object-fit:cover;object-fit:cover}.e-con-inner>.elementor-widget-video,.e-con>.elementor-widget-video{width:var(--container-widget-width);--flex-grow:var(--container-widget-flex-grow)}<\/style>\t\t<div class=\"elementor-wrapper elementor-open-inline\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-video\"><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2797384 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2797384\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 id=\"2-wordpress-features-easy-customization-in-regard-to-themes-and-plugins\">2: WordPress Features Easy Customization In Regard To Themes And Plugins<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-563a6be elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"563a6be\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">The 2nd Benefit of Wordpres is \u201c<a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/about\/features\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Its Features<\/a>\u201c. A vast majority of people relying on WordPress are new to WordPress website design. In addition, they don\u2019t have prior knowledge of WordPress development and website designing.<\/p><p class=\"look\">For non-tech savvy individuals, WordPress is the most sought-after solution as there are thousands of free website templates (themes) that they can pick from. There is an ideal WordPress theme\u00a0for just about every type of website (be it a blog, corporate site, or an e-commerce store).<\/p><p class=\"look\">WordPress themes can be customized easily because most of them come with their own selections panel enabling people to modify colors, upload logo, alter the background, design striking sliders, and perfectly customize it to their needs without getting into coding part at all.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0ca3c62 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"0ca3c62\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Advanced-customization.gif\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-19626\" alt=\"Advanced customization\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d6b74e4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d6b74e4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">Besides this, there is an option to add custom functionality to your website employing plugins. These plugins are like apps for your website that can be deployed for special elements such as analytics, contact forms, membership area, and more.<\/p><p class=\"look\">Alike WordPress themes, there are hundreds of free and pain plugins available.<\/p><p class=\"look\">Apart from including additional functionality, some WordPress plugins can allow you renovate your website into a totally new platform.<\/p><h3 id=\"3-wordpress-goes-along-with-seo\">3: WordPress Goes Along With SEO<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-38f0969 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"38f0969\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">The 3rd and most important benefit of WordPress is \u201cSEO\u201d. A WordPress website is made by using standard compliance high-quality code and results into semantic markup. In non-technical terms, WordPress websites are highly favored by Google and other search engines.<\/p><p>This is the reason why WordPress sites are found to rank better on search engines.<\/p><p>Both in terms of design and coding,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/searchenginewatch.com\/2017\/03\/21\/the-seo-benefits-of-using-wordpress-to-publish-your-content\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WordPress is favorable<\/a>. Moreover, you can optimize the website using various plugins and support your SEO efforts.<\/p><h3 id=\"4-wordpress-management-is-a-smoother-affair\">4: WordPress Management Is A Smoother Affair<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-069fd23 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"069fd23\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">The 4th benefit of wordpress is \u201cEasy to use\u201d. WordPress feature an in-built updates management system which allows users to update their plugins and themes right from their WordPress admin dashboard.<\/p><p class=\"look\">WordPress also informs you when there is a new version of WordPress is ready for download, so you can update your site by just clicking a button.<\/p><p class=\"look\">To safeguard your data from any hacking or accident, you can feasibly use a WordPress backup plugin to automatically generate backups and store them comfortably on a different system.<\/p><p class=\"look\">You can also manage your WordPress site on the go using WordPress mobile apps.<\/p><h3 id=\"5-wordpress-is-safe-for-use\">5: WordPress Is Safe For Use<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-190b601 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"190b601\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">The 5th wordpres benefit we are going to know is \u201cWordPress Security\u201d. When it comes to ensure security of your website and data, WordPress is a trustworthy partner. According to experts, it is an extremely safe and secure website development platform. However, nobody knows how things can turn awkwardly on internet.<\/p><p class=\"look\">There are various steps you can take to increase the security quotient of your website.<\/p><p><strong>Also Check<\/strong>\u00a0:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/facebook-page-promotion\/\">How To Promote A Facebook Business Page?<\/a><\/p><h3 id=\"6-managing-different-media-types-is-easy-with-wordpress\">6: Managing Different Media Types Is Easy With WordPress<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c7b9329 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c7b9329\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">Number 6 benefit of a wordpress website is its \u201cMedia Uploader\u201d. Keep in mind that WordPress is a lot more effective than just writing text. It features an in-built media uploader that can be used to manage images, video, and audio files.<\/p><p class=\"look\">WordPress supports Embed activated websites which means you can embed YouTube videos, Instagram photos, Tweets, and Soundcloud audio by just typing the URL in the WordPress post editor.<\/p><p class=\"look\">What types of websites you can make using WordPress?<\/p><p class=\"look\">WordPress can be employed in a number of ways for making simple websites to full-fledged e-commerce stores.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-afb4c9c elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"afb4c9c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/website-cost-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-19414\" alt=\"website-cost\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/website-cost-1.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/website-cost-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/website-cost-1-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-63bee98 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"63bee98\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 id=\"how-does-wordpress-work\">How Does WordPress Work?<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2436b57 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2436b57\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">As we all know wordpress is a very easy CMS and you can divide it in 3 parts.<\/p><ul><li><strong>Content:<\/strong>\u00a0You can create post and page easily with the help of post editor<\/li><li><strong>Design:<\/strong>\u00a0You can use many FREE wordpress themes to design your wordpress website.<\/li><li><strong>Plugins\/Addons:<\/strong>\u00a0Plugins make wordpress more beneficial for its users. If you want to add any feature in your wordpress website then you only need to find the plugin from plugin store. Just install and activate it and you are done.<\/li><\/ul><h3 id=\"who-should-use-wordpress-is-it-right-for-you\">Who Should Use WordPress? Is it Right for You?<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9606201 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9606201\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">The most important benefit of wordpress website is it can be modified as per your requirements. You can make it simple if you not that technical and you can also customize it if you have knowledge of wordpress and familiar with wordpress features.<br \/>Here is the checklist if you want to know if wordpress is right for you or not:<\/p><ul><li>You can use wordpress if you have a limited budget but want a quick and easy to use website for your business.<\/li><li>If you are not familiar with coding and website development then you can watch some wordpress tutorial videos on Youtube to learn the basics to build a website using wordpress. So you don\u2019t need to hire any\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/web-development-company-india\/wordpress-development-company-india\/\">wordpress development company<\/a>.<\/li><li>You can take advantage of wordpress if you dont want to spend money on\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/website-maintenance-packages\/\">website maintenance<\/a>.<\/li><\/ul><h3 id=\"who-should-not-use-wordpress\">Who Should Not Use WordPress?<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-527ff1c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"527ff1c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>You may not like wordpress if you want :<\/p><ul><li>High Security<\/li><li>Fast Loading<\/li><li>High Performance<\/li><\/ul><h3 id=\"what-kind-of-websites-you-can-build-using-wordpress\">What Kind of Websites You Can Build Using WordPress<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-90d79e9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"90d79e9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>For example, you can use WordPress to:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Make a Blog website<\/li><li>Make a business website<\/li><li>Create an online store<\/li><li>Build a membership website<\/li><li>Sell online courses<\/li><\/ul><p class=\"look\"><strong>I hope you like this article, if yes, don\u2019t forget to like it and leave a comment below. Contact\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/\">Rankon Technologies<\/a>\u00a0Now!<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"look\">If you are searching for\u00a0a Web Design Company in India\u00a0then look no further than RankOn Technologies- A Trusted\u00a0Web Development Company in India\u00a0for all your website-related needs. Visit our\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/website-development-packages-india\/\">website development packages<\/a>\u00a0now!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Whether you\u2019re looking to develop a new website or want to revamp an existing one, one of the most widely asked questions is \u2013 which CMS platform is ideal for your project. And in most of the cases, the most prominent answer that comes out is WordPress. But why there is so much craze of &hellip;<\/p>\n<p class=\"read-more\"> <a class=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wordpress-benefits\/\"> <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">WordPress Benefits: WordPress Website Advantages &#038; Its SEO Benefits in 2024<\/span> Read More &raquo;<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author"